    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>A multi-colored scattering of bio-plastic flakes adds a celebratory flair to the Jetpack's output. Expelled material is fully compostable.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
